Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1\n0\n0\N{\fs19}{\fnsimhei}{\frz7}{\c&H0F0F0F&}{\3c&H4B59D8&}{\pos(188,300)}必\n須\n熟\n記\n的\n定\n式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井 你在幹嘛!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然看著書下!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有犯規…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因為總捧著它下得才那麼差的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方不按書來下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定式那種東西根本就派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然清楚了 可是沒書的話我就心裏沒底…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的 安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 不要再惹人注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了按計時器了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好心吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是絕配
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是連計時器都沒見過的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是只會按書下棋的白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個是從將棋社跑來湊數的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一回合可以輕鬆取勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要下 小光 好嘛好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別分心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 兩勝才能晉級
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個一定可以贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也為森山可惜 但是對方太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 讓我來看看這傢伙的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 亂七八糟的差勁死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那個排山倒海的追擊是亂猜的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我下的 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想認真下啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的實力不只這樣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你在玩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:18:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋盤上有9個「星」對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我呢 把棋子一個一個放上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像添上一顆又一顆星星一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在創造宇宙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像神一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這個棋盤上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還要下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想下 不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}但是勝負不是已經很明顯了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都陪你玩累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才小光的復棋 難道只是偶然?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為在小光身上\n看到了和塔矢亮一樣的圍棋天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是一勝一敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠筒井了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【GoGo】
